"4 cups canola oil","4.4 ounces gluten-free all-purpose flour (about 1 cup; such as Bob's Red Mill)","5 ounces white rice flour (about 1 cup; such as Bob's Red Mill)","1 tablespoon chili powder","1 teaspoon baking soda","1 1/4 cups club soda, chilled","1  medium onion, cut into 1/2-inch-thick slices and separated into rings (8 ounces)","1/4 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon garlic powder","1/4 teaspoon black pepper","1/2 cup ketchup (optional)"